name: Neon union
description: Gossip slacker is the third type we’re going to talk about today. This species can be quite dangerous, often working on a word of radio is its main activity. Sometimes the words are bright and saturated with poison. It follows from his name that because of his lack of work and hobbies, he has no choice but to envy others and to spread foul and false gossip. Slackers tend to belittle people in the eyes of others because they have low self-esteem and want to look better than the subject matter.
